data.description: Nestled on a tranquil corner lot, this remarkable residence offers the perfect blend of privacy and convenience. Boasting not one, but two master suites, two spacious living rooms, and two fully equipped kitchens, this home is a haven for those seeking flexibility and versatility in their living arrangements. Enjoy the luxury of two master bedroom retreats, each offering an oasis of relaxation with private ensuite bathrooms. Whether you're hosting guests or accommodating a multi-generational household, these master suites provide the ultimate in comfort and convenience.  With two distinct living areas, this home provides endless possibilities for entertaining, relaxation, or even creating separate spaces for work and play.  The corner lot provides extra yard space and privacy for outdoor gatherings, gardening, or simply unwinding in a serene setting.  There is already a 30 amp electric hookup for an RV there for you.  Whether you desire a private retreat, a multi-generational haven, or an income-generating investment, this home delivers on every front. The roof was replaced in 2018 and all new Renewal by Anderson windows throughout the whole house in 2023.  SELLER WILL CONTRIBUTE $2500.00 TOWARDS THE BUYERS CLOSING COSTS!
